3.30 pm At 3.30 I went home from school in the car. When I got home I got a phone call from Elizabeth. She asked me if I wanted to go to her house for tea. I said "Yes", so my mum took me to her house. We played in the back garden for awhile, then we had tea. We had mince, potato and peas. 7.00 pm When I had finished it was nearly time for me to go home. When it was 7.00 I went home and watched telly for awhile. I saw Tomorrow's World, Top of the Pops and Little and Large.
9.00 pm At 9.00 I went to bed.
{Maria Turner ( 9 years ) }
